Class CashInBunker

  • java.lang.Object
    • master.CashInBunker

  • public class CashInBunker
extends java.lang.Object
    The amount of money paid should be in here at least via the form of coupons, checks, and cash. Should have a return value of the total amount inside. Original abstract of MoneyBunker has been removed. This is it's replacement.
